---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Global Hope India — Vision, Mission & Story"
  description="Global Hope India exists to see Indian Nationals transformed into ambassadors for the gospel. Learn our vision, mission, values, and 25-year history."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "AboutPage",
      "name": "About Global Hope India",
      "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org/about",
      "description": "Vision, mission, values, and history of Global Hope India"
    })}></script>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- ── HERO ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[65vh] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src="https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/images/ghi-about-hero.webp"
      alt="Indian young people"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-[center_30%]"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pb-10 pt-64">
      <h1 class="text-[#2EAB5A] max-w-3xl font-bold text-[26px] md:text-[30px] lg:text-[50px] leading-[1.3] lg:leading-[1.2] ">Church Vision and Mission:<br/>Shaping Faith's Future with<br/>Global Hope India</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── VISION / EMPOWERING / MISSION ROW ───────────────── -->
  <section class="relative section bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 items-start">
        <!-- Our Vision -->
        <div class="text-center px-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-[#FEC415]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#FEC415]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.182 15.182a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364 0M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zM9.75 9.75c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75S9 10.164 9 9.75 9.168 9 9.375 9s.375.336.375.75zm-.375 0h.008v.015h-.008V9.75zm5.625 0c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75s-.375-.336-.375-.75.168-.75.375-.75.375.336.375.75zm-.375 0h.008v.015h-.008V9.75z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Our Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">"Everyone in India worshiping Jesus as Savior and Lord."</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Empowering Radical Transformation -->
        <div class="text-center px-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-[#FEC415]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#FEC415]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 21L3 16.5m0 0L7.5 12M3 16.5h13.5m0-13.5L21 7.5m0 0L16.5 12M21 7.5H7.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Empowering Radical Transformation</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">For over 25 years, we have been watching God radically transform thousands of Americans &amp; Indian Nationals through missions. We've taken over 1,000 Americans on short-term mission trips to India. We work with 12 long-term indigenous church-planting partners located in North, South, East, &amp; West Mainland India as well as Northeast India. We empower The Church in India to make Christ known through leadership, child, &amp; village development projects.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Mission -->
        <div class="text-center px-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-[#FEC415]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#FEC415]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">"Global Hope India exists to see Indian Nationals, absent to the gospel, transformed into ambassadors for the gospel."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Large green swoosh at bottom-right -->
    <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 pointer-events-none opacity-50">
      <svg width="200" height="120" viewBox="0 0 200 120" fill="none"><path d="M10 90c40-80 120-80 180-20" stroke="#2EAB5A" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/><path d="M170 55l22 15-20 8" fill="#2EAB5A"/></svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── OUR CULTURE ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative section bg-[#F8F5EF] overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Large faded green circle decoration -->
    <div class="absolute -left-32 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-[#2EAB5A]/10 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] mb-10">Our Culture</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-0">
        <!-- Left column: items 1-4 -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">1.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We are missionaries.</strong> It's about being sent out by God; for the purposes of God, to the glory of God.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">2.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We love India.</strong> It's about Jesus' love for every nation, tribe, and tongue, absent to the gospel.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">3.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We facilitate short-term mission trips to India.</strong> It's about our radical response for the love &amp; grace we've received.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">4.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We empower The Church to fulfill the Great Commission.</strong> It's about Jesus' love for His bride — the Big C Church.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right column: items 5-9 -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">5.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We minimize distractions.</strong> It's about freeing you to focus on the mission.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">6.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We stand on God's Word.</strong> It's about His Word being for all people and us hearing &amp; obeying the voice of God.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">7.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We make prayer — the work.</strong> It's about salvation belonging to God and Him doing the work in and through us.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">8.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We honor the Holy Spirit.</strong> It's about experiencing God and joining Him in His work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold text-lg mt-0.5 shrink-0">9.</span>
            <p class="text-[#1D1C1C] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[#2EAB5A]">We live generously.</strong> It's about worship and providing an attractive witness of the gospel.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── DID SOMEONE SAY RADICAL? ─────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">
        <!-- Left: group photo -->
        <div>
          <img
            src="https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/images/ghi-radical-group.jpg"
            alt="Global Hope India mission team under covered structure"
            class="rounded-lg w-full h-auto object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Right: text content -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Did Someone Say, "Radical"?</h2>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-[1.8] mb-5">
            Today, India is 72% Hindu, 23% Muslim, 3% Christian and 2% other faiths. We believe God can take this country known for its persecution of Christians and radically transform India to be one of the largest church planters in our day.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-[1.8]">
            We believe God can transform a Saul into a Paul! (Acts 9) Therefore, we are on a mission to see God transform India, from being unreached by the Gospel to being reached by the Gospel. But, not just reached! We believe God can transform India, from receiving missionaries to sending missionaries! Our vision is for God to transform India, from being a people known for their poverty, to a Church known for its generosity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── ACCORDION 2x2 GRID ────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Left column -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Why India? -->
          <div class="accordion-card bg-[#F5F5EE] rounded-xl p-6">
            <button class="accordion-btn w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left" aria-expanded="true">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1D1C1C]">Why India?</h3>
              <span class="accordion-sign text-[#1D1C1C] text-2xl leading-none shrink-0 ml-4">—</span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-body mt-4">
              <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">With 1.4 billion people, India represents one of the largest, neediest, and most unreached countries in the world.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Changing The World -->
          <div class="accordion-card bg-[#F5F5EE] rounded-xl p-6">
            <button class="accordion-btn w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left" aria-expanded="true">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1D1C1C]">Changing The World</h3>
              <span class="accordion-sign text-[#1D1C1C] text-2xl leading-none shrink-0 ml-4">—</span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-body mt-4">
              <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">In 1972, in his only crusade ever in India, Dr. Billy Graham said, "As India goes, all of Asia will go with her." In essence, he was saying: that if we can make Christ known among the 1.4 billion people of India, they will help us to make Christ known among the 4.6 billion people in Asia. Not only does that cover the entire 10/40 window, but that is 2/3's of the earth's total population!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right column -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- The Big "C" Church -->
          <div class="accordion-card bg-[#F5F5EE] rounded-xl p-6">
            <button class="accordion-btn w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left" aria-expanded="true">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1D1C1C]">The Big "C" Church</h3>
              <span class="accordion-sign text-[#1D1C1C] text-2xl leading-none shrink-0 ml-4">—</span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-body mt-4">
              <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">EVERYTHING we do is through the local church! Jesus said, "I will build my Church, and the gates of hell will not prevail against it." (Matthew 16:18) We believe history proves the most effective means of evangelism and it is the starting of new churches. Therefore, we empower The Church in India to train more healthy church-planting pastors that will start more healthy churches.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Living The Dream -->
          <div class="accordion-card bg-[#F5F5EE] rounded-xl p-6">
            <button class="accordion-btn w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left" aria-expanded="true">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1D1C1C]">Living The Dream</h3>
              <span class="accordion-sign text-[#1D1C1C] text-2xl leading-none shrink-0 ml-4">—</span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-body mt-4">
              <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">We help The Church be on earth as it is in heaven. In Revelation 7:9-12, we see the Church in heaven filled with people from every nation, tongue, and tribe gathered around the throne worshiping Jesus.</p>
              <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm mt-3">Won't you join us in living the dream?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-btn').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const card = btn.closest('.accordion-card');
        const body = card?.querySelector('.accordion-body');
        const sign = btn.querySelector('.accordion-sign');
        const isOpen = btn.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
        if (isOpen) {
          body?.classList.add('hidden');
          btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
          if (sign) sign.textContent = '+';
        } else {
          body?.classList.remove('hidden');
          btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
          if (sign) sign.textContent = '—';
        }
      });
    });
  </script>

  <!-- ── 4 WAYS WE EMPOWER BELIEVERS ─────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section bg-[#F5F5EE]">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-10">4 Ways we Empower Believers Globally</h2>
      <ol class="space-y-3 text-[#444]">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="font-bold text-[#1D1C1C]">1.</span>
          <p>Pray for Believers (Americans &amp; Indians) to receive &amp; share Christ.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="font-bold text-[#1D1C1C]">2.</span>
          <p>Give to God's work through GHI.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="font-bold text-[#1D1C1C]">3.</span>
          <p>Go and serve the Church in India.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="font-bold text-[#1D1C1C]">4.</span>
          <p>Resources for radical transformation.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <!-- 2x2 Card Grid: Pray, Give, Go, Resources -->
      <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12">
        <!-- Pray -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#FEC415] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Pray</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">Salvation and transformation are God's work. Our work is to pray. We empower you to engage in God's work by praying very specifically for the people of India. Everyone wants to make a difference in the world. Changing the World is a daunting task, but when we pray and obey God, He can change our world forever.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Give -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#FEC415] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Give</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">We empower you to engage by giving generously and sacrificially to God's work through GHI. God uses every gift to GHI so that Americans and Indian Nationals are radically transformed by &amp; for The Gospel. Over 85% of every dollar given directly benefits our programs here in the USA and India.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Go -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#FEC415] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Go</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">We believe one of the most radical ways for us to engage in God's mission is to get on a plane and go to India. Few things are more endearing to any International living in the USA than the words, "I've been there." We empower you to go and share the love and grace you've been shown.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Resources -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#FEC415] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">4</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Resources</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed text-sm">We empower church staffs and volunteers with an identifiable and measurable strategy for reaching the internationals in their community. When our churches reach foreign-born internationals, they will reach other foreign-born nationals. Now that is truly changing the world!</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Green swoosh bottom-right -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 pointer-events-none opacity-40 hidden md:block">
          <svg width="180" height="100" viewBox="0 0 180 100" fill="none"><path d="M10 80c40-70 110-70 160-15" stroke="#2EAB5A" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/><path d="M152 50l20 15-18 6" fill="#2EAB5A"/></svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 3 WAYS OUR TEAMS SERVE ──────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-center mb-12">3 Ways Our Teams Serve The Church in India</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Leadership Development -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-[#2EAB5A]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-[#2EAB5A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Leadership Development</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed">We equip church planters, pastors, worship leaders, church staff, and core leaders with biblical truth &amp; practical resources.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Child Development -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-[#2EAB5A]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-[#2EAB5A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Child Development</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed">We empower the local church as they make Christ known among children in schools, orphan homes, and local communities.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Community Development -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-[#2EAB5A]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-[#2EAB5A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Community Development</h3>
          <p class="text-[#555] leading-relaxed">We empower local churches in India with clean water projects, hygiene kits, business development projects, and other practical resources.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── HOW GHI BEGAN ────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <!-- Row 1: Text left, Photo right -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start mb-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">How GHI Began</h2>
          <div class="space-y-5 text-[#444] leading-relaxed">
            <p>During our founder's first trip to India in 1998, God planted a part of his heart in India. He returned three years later, with his 11-year-old son, and again three years after that, with his 11-year-old daughter.</p>
            <p>In 2003, GHI incorporated as a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization for the sole purpose of having a bank account and the ability to offer donors a tax-deductible receipt.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img
